Nestled in the vibrant heart of Brooklyn, Phoenix Falls Café is all about fantastic brews, delicious breakfast, and a welcoming atmosphere.

Our mission is to provide a haven where locals and visitors alike can savor the best coffee and breakfast offerings in town. Everything we make is done passion and care, so we guarantee you'll leave with a smile.
